### =====================================================================
### DEBT-1. 代码债清理验证补充
### =====================================================================

### DEBT-1-W1. F6 审核通过 1001 后重新登录，roles 应包含 jst_channel
POST {{baseUrl}}/jst/wx/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{ "code": "MOCK_1001" }

> {%
client.global.set("wx_token", response.body.data.token);
client.test("DEBT-1 wx login roles 应来自 sys_user_role", function() {
    client.assert(response.body.code === 200);
    client.assert(Array.isArray(response.body.data.roles));
    client.assert(response.body.data.roles.includes("jst_channel"), "应有 jst_channel 角色");
});
%}

### DEBT-1-W2. 补件后查看详情，supplementRemark 应落在独立字段
